This paper deals with emotion analysis and natural language processing, which are typically covered under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of embeddings and semantic spaces, which are relevant to the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
